ik a magnetik, vzorové výpočty."]},"tutorialsContentsEn":{"line":["1.\tExercise schedule and introduction to laboratory exercises.","2.\tThe temperature dependence of the conductors and semiconductors conductivity.","3.\tThe measurements of the complex permittivity of the dielectric.","4.\tThe magnetic properties as a function of the frequency of applied field.","5.\tThe crystal structure and properties, examples for computations.","6.\tThe properties of conductors and semiconductors, examples for computations.","7.\tThe properties of dielectrics and magnetics, example for computations. Credits."]}}